Network: BNB Smart Chain (BSC)

Background and Rationale

The originally deployed CSJ smart contract could not be verified on-chain due to technical constraints unrelated to supply intent, allocation design, or custodial principles.

To ensure long-term transparency, auditability, and historical clarity, a new smart contract was deployed and successfully verified on BscScan.

This action constitutes a technical migration for verification purposes and does not represent a reset, expansion, or alteration of the White Paper v1 genesis supply.

Canonical Genesis Supply (Unchanged)

The White Paper v1 defined a fixed and indivisible genesis supply of 369,000 CSJ, which remains unchanged and canonized.

